Class YearlyData

  • java.lang.Object
    • StatisticsAbstract
      • MultiStatisticsAbstract
        • YearlyData

  • public class YearlyData
extends MultiStatisticsAbstract
    Author:
    CS2334. Modified by: Will Booker, David Jones

    Date: 2015-09-28
    Project 3

    This class is a representation of a year's worth of statistics. This class comes with an array list that holds twelve Monthly Data objects.
